name: Save Do Kwon DAO
description:
Save Do Kwon!
The warrant issued by the Korean government has completely violated what blockchain represents for. 
The DAO will be contributed for the purpose of hiring superior attorneys as well as any bail fees if required by Do Kwon.
This is not just a protest from blockchain but also an revolution against the centralized governments!

We have been in touch with Luna Foundation Guard (LFG) in regards to specific schemes on saving Do Kwon, and raised funds from serval communities. The birth of Bitcoin was where blockchain starts its revolution, and we are the next savior.
